name: 【Costume】Race Queen Outfit of Shoukaku and Zuikaku (Azur Lane) 翔鹤与瑞鹤的赛车女郎装
description:
I made Shoukaku (Race Queen)‘s lora long time ago. Well at that time I was really a noob who did not know how to handle with datasets and trigger words.

This lora is for cosplaying Shoukaku and Zuikaku (Race Queen). If you just input "white hair, very long hair", Shoukaku might show up(

Shoukaku's hairstyle can not be recognized as a tag in tagger, so you might got a tiny side ponytail sometimes. It's suggested to add "side_ponytail" and "one_side_up" to Negative Prompts if you do not want that.

很久以前我做了翔鹤（赛车女郎）的lora。不过当时我是纯萌新菜鸡，不知道如何处理数据集和触发词。

这个lora是用于cosplay翔鹤和瑞鹤的。如果你输入"white hair, very long hair", 翔鹤可能会出现。

翔鹤的发型，tagger打不出标来，所以有时候你可能会得到一个小小的侧辫子。如果你不想要的话，建议把"side_ponytail" 和 "one_side_up" 扔进反咒里。
